commit.message: Bump libh2o dependency (because of h2o_expand()).
Add expand() method for expansion calcs.
Fix potentially non-terminated list.

Split Py2/3 module init into separate files.

This should be more readable.
Move common initialization bits out of main func.
Rename module init function for Py3.
Clean up return values for Py3.
Support Py3 module initialization API.
Use PyVarObject_HEAD_INIT for py3 compat.
Bump devel status.
Support getting region.
Raise ValueError when trying to get x in R3.

Disallow uninitialized H2O.

Python's not strict-typed, no need for such a thing.
Add MANIFEST to gitignore.
Support getting medium properties.
Support initiating the H2O type.
Initiate the codebase.
